<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19728906">为什么身体动作有调整心理的效果？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="71657" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"> 比如在心理治疗的时候，心理治疗师会让人通过一些身体动作来帮助病人。<br>瑜伽也是通过身体的动作来调整人的心理状态。<br>这是否跟神经科学相关？ </div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

<a href="#" name="addcomment" class="toggle-comment meta-item">
<i class="z-icon-comment"></i>1 条评论
</a>
<a href="#" name="share" class="share meta-item">
<i class="z-icon-share"></i>分享
</a>

</div>
<div class="panel-container">

</div>
</div>
